@Quick_Gen_HostAddress = http://localhost:5176

### Health (no auth)
GET {{Quick_Gen_HostAddress}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Register (Student role)
POST {{Quick_Gen_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "اختبار الطالب",
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "Abcd1234"
}

###

### Login
POST {{Quick_Gen_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student@example.com",
  "password": "Abcd1234"
}

###

### Me (paste Bearer token from login response)
GET {{Quick_Gen_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN
Accept: application/json

###
